U.S. OPEN CHAMPIONSHIP
June 17, 2012
Webb Simpson
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







Q.   What's your first reaction?
WEBB SIMPSON:   Amazed.   I've got no words.   Just thankful to God.   I couldn't have done it without him.

Q.   That was so much golf, so much faith.   How do you combine the two?
WEBB SIMPSON:   It controls everything. 







END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT